# Parser Development

## Adding a New Platform

1. Add platform constant to [model/platform.go](mdc:internal/model/platform.go)
2. Create parser in `internal/parser/<platform>/`
3. Implement `Parser` interface from [parser/parser.go](mdc:internal/parser/parser.go)
4. Register in [parser/tiered/factories.go](mdc:internal/parser/tiered/factories.go)

## Parser Interface
```go
type Parser interface {
    Parse() ([]model.Skill, error)
    Platform() model.Platform
    DefaultPath() string
}
```

